i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我帶路"},{"pid":"fc0c9a3b2f39e10f4d3de48e4510ad36dd66323f","tid":1460022,"uid":128923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"順便一提，美國國會中國委員會，rubio係副主席，主席係民主黨既Jim McGovern，佢都有留心臥底同爆眼：<br />\n<br />\nDue to the excessive use of force &amp; lack of restraint by #HongKong authorities, <span style=\"color: red;\">I will soon introduce legislation to suspend U.S. sales of munitions, police &amp; crowd control equipment to the #HongKong police</span>.<br />\n<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern<br />\n@RepMcGovern<br />\n1/ I am appalled and outraged by #HongKong police and their escalating violence and brutality towards peaceful protesters and journalists.<span style=\"color: red;\"> I pray in particular for the young woman who was shot in her eye with a beanbag round at close range</span>.<br />\n<br />\n2/ The whole world is watching in real time. <span style=\"color: red;\">We know the truth and we will not be fooled by attempts to demonize these protesters. </span>#HongKong authorities should not adopt mainland China&rsquo;s tactics of suppression.<br />\n<br />\n3/ I call on #CarrieLam to immediately begin a dialogue with protest leaders to address their legitimate grievances including <span style=\"color: red;\">withdrawing the extradition bill, ending police violence &amp; granting universal suffrage</span>. The only way forward is peaceful dialogue &ndash; not more violence.<br />\n<br />\n4/ I also<span style=\"color: red;\"> call on the Trump administration</span> to stop sending mixed signals on #HongKong. Instead,<span style=\"color: red;\"> they should suspend transfers of police &amp; crowd control equipment to Hong Kong police</span>. America must be on the side of those peacefully protesting for democracy and the rule of law."},{"pid":"5d0ac81d79371e67728fd7b2e2df0951c6fb715d","tid":1460022,"uid":26810